{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a490fb2fc","title":"中共中央对被批判斗争对象的工资处理问题的通知","origin":"根据文件的翻印件，翻印者未注明","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"df06f96a5c","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"7a490fb2fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ca47270b03","name":"吉林文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b5ba5aa342","type":"title","text":"中共中央对被批判斗争对象的工资处理问题的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a490fb2fc"},{"id":"382e16238b","type":"appellation","text":"吉林省委并东北局，各中央局：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a490fb2fc"},{"id":"d6d9ea0747","type":"paragraph","text":"吉林省委九月十六日电悉。对被批判斗争对象的工资处理意见，即使已定性的，也暂不改变，如本人少领工资，或捐献一部分工资作党费，听其自愿，但不强求，也不许其由减少用费而致病；私人东西，除政治性的，一般不查抄；凡未定性的，工资仍照旧。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a490fb2fc"}],"page":{"id":"23473afc41","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7a490fb2fc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}